headline: Assessing Domino’s After the Uber Eats Partnership and Recent Share Price Moves
summary: Thinking about whether Domino's Pizza stock is a hidden gem or priced just right? You are not alone, as many investors are taking a closer look at whether the current price reflects the company's true potential. Despite climbing 0.6% over the past week and 0.7% this month, Domino's Pizza shares are still down 5.9% so far this year after a 16.4% gain over three years. This makes it an intriguing time to revisit the story. Recently, Domino's unveiled a new delivery partnership with Uber Eats,...
